item.title: Contributions: MS Office 2003
item.description: This time a double-win. Not so long ago trying to run a whole office suite was almost a dream. Just launching an app was a success.There was just one complex suite almost working: "SoftMaker Office 2008". A nice, and mostly unknown, Microsoft Office clone. It was such a good Office clone that it is closed and non-free. From past experience you can find two kind of users out there: "Pro-open source"
